Alive Wellness Centre CIC
We help the survivors of knife crime and youth violence via counselling services, physical activities like personal training regimes, in youth clubs and community centres across Birmingham.
We specialise in helping kids gain self confidence in dealing with aggression and have partnered with Krav4Kids who teach basic self defence skills, and Kieran Wood
We work in conjuction with partners like: BBC Children in Need. The Crime Commissioner's Office Violence Reduction Partnership.  ASDA.  LoveBrum.  West Midlands Police.  The UK National Lottery (Millions Hour Fund).  SportsEngland.
